      • isShared

        default boolean isShared()

        Tell if this is shared.

        Data and functions whose call() method returns this as well as simple boxes that just hold a value ready to be supplied and Thunks are considered shared.

        But a bare lambda expression is assumed to be in need of sharing. For example:

        () -> 42
        Returns:
        false, if sharing this would make any sense, otherwise true
